Global Payment Technologies Australia Pty Ltd (GPT) is an Australian company that was incorporated in 1997. The company designs, manufactures, sells and supports payment components internationally. GPT carries a full range of payment components and specialises in innovative note validation and payment components for the international Gaming, Vending, Parking and Kiosk industries.
